This is a request to allow users to set a default month when inserting a team calendar into a wiki page. For example, an organizer might create an event calendar for a conference which is scheduled several months into the future, such as January 2013. The lead organizer might want to create a wiki page where other planners can view the latest schedule for the conference, and contribute to its updates. It would be easier for everyone to show the month of the conference on this wiki page by default, instead of showing the current, empty month, and requiring organizers to manually scroll to the correct month each time they load the page.

Thanks for considering it!

